Package card.game

Class Summary
CardGame CardGame is the superclass for WarGame and PokerGame.
Hand Hand class is the superclass for various kinds of card game hands.
MainClass  
Player Player is the superclass for various kinds of CardGame players.
PokerGame PokerGame is a subclass of CardGame.
PokerHand PokerHand represents a 5 card poker hand.
PokerPlayer PokerPlayer is the simplistic representation of a poker player.
PokerRanker PokerRanker is a helper class.
PokerRankWithHighCards PokerRankWithHighCards is a value class to hold the evaluated rank (an enum value) and the kickers needed to break a potential tie.
WarGame WarGame is a subclass of CardGame.

This is a children's game with no real strategy.
WarHand WarHand represents the state of a war player's hand at some point in the game.
